flowchart TD

User[User Natural Language Query]

User --> APIGW[API Gateway]

APIGW --> Orchestrator[Query Orchestrator]

Orchestrator --> DomainSelector[Domain Selector]

DomainSelector --> DomainRegistry[Domain Registry]

DomainRegistry --> CloudDomain[Cloud Resources Domain]
DomainRegistry --> ApiDomain[API Inventory Domain]
DomainRegistry --> ChangeDomain[Change Logs Domain]

CloudDomain --> Catalog1[Dataset Catalog]
ApiDomain --> Catalog2[Dataset Catalog]
ChangeDomain --> Catalog3[Dataset Catalog]

Catalog1 --> ContextBuilder
Catalog2 --> ContextBuilder
Catalog3 --> ContextBuilder

ContextBuilder --> VectorSearch[Vector Search / Semantic Retrieval]

VectorSearch --> EntityResolver[Entity Resolver]

EntityResolver --> Planner

Planner[LLM Planner NL → QuerySpec]

Planner --> Validator[QuerySpec Validator]

Validator --> CostGuard[Query Cost Guardrail]

CostGuard --> Resolver[Dataset Resolver]

Resolver --> SQLBuilder[SQL Builder AST]

SQLBuilder --> CacheCheck{Query Cache}

CacheCheck -->|Hit| Formatter
CacheCheck -->|Miss| DBExec

DBExec --> CloudDB[(Cloud Resource DB)]
DBExec --> ApiDB[(API Inventory DB)]
DBExec --> ChangeDB[(Change Logs DB)]

CloudDB --> CacheStore[Cache Result]
ApiDB --> CacheStore
ChangeDB --> CacheStore

CacheStore --> Formatter

Formatter[Response Formatter]

Formatter --> Response[User Response]

Orchestrator --> Observability[Logs / Metrics / Audit]

Observability --> Monitoring[(Monitoring System)]
